title: LEAFY ROTISSERIE CHICKEN SALAD WITH CREAMY TARRAGON DRESSING
directions: Add 1/2 cup of the beans, the vinegar, oil, garlic, and 1 Tbsp. of the tarragon to a blender. Cover and puree.
Arrange greens on a large platter. Top with remaining beans, onion, chicken, grapes, cucumber, nuts, pepper, and remaining 1 Tbsp. tarragon.
Serve the dressing on the side.
